{"tid":2093299,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇聞重溫]國家發改委原司長高俊才為三峽工程寫了打油詩","createTime":"2020-07-03T17:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T17:58:14.000Z","uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"520c2249c9f85d9eb1038838a83ee940570e341b","tid":2093299,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:39:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ndrc.gov.cn/xwdt/gdzt/cl70zn/201909/t20190930_1197749_ext.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndrc.gov.cn%2Fxwdt%2Fgdzt%2Fcl70zn%2F201909%2Ft20190930_1197749_ext.html&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IKF0%2BEjl5hukozrtPJpxOa8%3D&h=babdeb5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ndrc.gov.cn/xwdt/gdzt/cl70zn/201909/t20190930_1197749_ext.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【三峽工程&mdash;&mdash;承載著幾代人夢想的世紀工程】<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國家發展改革委農經司原司長 高俊才為精彩神奇的三峽工程寫了打油詩</span><br />\n<br />\n（一）<br />\n<br />\n瞿塘夔門巫山雲，西陵大壩真雄峻。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>天人合一造奇物，百年夢想今成真。</ins><br />\n<br />\n（二）<br />\n<br />\n萬里長江第一壩，<ins>除害興利效益大。</ins><br />\n<br />\n規模宏偉驚世界，<ins>高峽平湖潤中華。<br />\n</ins><br />\n（三）<br />\n<br />\n滔滔江水生金銀，浩浩船隊過夔門。<br />\n<br />\n長江防洪增保障，<ins>多效造福數億人。</ins><br />\n<br />\n（四）<br />\n<br />\n天兵開出&ldquo;第四峽&rdquo;，神匠建成五級閘。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>水落水漲一百米</ins>，萬噸船隊過三峽。<br />\n<br />\n（注：&ldquo;第四峽&rdquo;和&ldquo;五級閘&rdquo;都是指三峽永久船閘。）<br />\nSānxi&aacute; gōngch&eacute;ng"},{"pid":"a96e548498d473aed673ed50cb0a1c889b8c55ba","tid":2093299,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"有暗喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}